{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Design a luxury “Latest Arrivals” product showcase section for a fashion or lifestyle e-commerce website.
    
    Layout & structure:
    – Section title aligned left: “Our Latest Arrivals”
    – Two minimal text tabs aligned right: “New Arrivals” (active) and “Best Sellers” (inactive)
    – Horizontal product grid with 4 product cards visible on desktop
    – Each product card includes a full-height lifestyle image on a neutral background
    
    Product card details:
    – Product name below image
    – Price displayed clearly under product name
    – Small color swatches shown beneath price
    – Optional small “New” tag on the top corner of one card
    – No ratings, no reviews, no discount badges
    
    Interaction & hover behavior:
    – On hover, product image subtly elevates or softens
    – Color swatches highlight smoothly on hover
    – No aggressive zoom or motion
    – Smooth transitions (150–250ms ease-in-out)
    
    Tabs behavior:
    – Clicking “New Arrivals” or “Best Sellers” filters products dynamically
    – Active tab has a thin underline or darker text
    – No heavy animation between tab switches
    
    Style & tone:
    – Editorial, fashion-forward, premium
    – Clean typography with strong hierarchy
    – Plenty of white space
    – Soft neutral backgrounds
    – Designed to feel like a high-end fashion lookbook, not a marketplace
    
    UX rules:
    – Entire product card is clickable
    – Interactions should feel calm and intentional
    – Avoid clutter, urgency, or promotional language,  I want to have an option to keep my tabs center aligned, I want center aligned option for mobile view as well, I need title also in the center on mobile
{% enddoc %}
